Dependencies for ikafssn
========================

Runtime dependencies (pre-built binaries)
------------------------------------------

Ubuntu 24.04 (x86_64 / aarch64):

  libtbb12
  liblmdb0
  libsqlite3-0
  libcurl4
  libjsoncpp25
  zlib1g
  libbz2-1.0
  liblzma5
  libdeflate0

  Additional for ikafssnhttpd:
    libdrogon (and its transitive dependencies)

Ubuntu 22.04 (x86_64 / aarch64):

  libtbb12
  liblmdb0
  libsqlite3-0
  libcurl4
  libjsoncpp24
  zlib1g
  libbz2-1.0
  liblzma5
  libdeflate0

  Note: ikafssnhttpd is not available on Ubuntu 22.04
  (Drogon is not packaged for this release).

macOS 26 (aarch64, Homebrew):

  tbb
  lmdb
  sqlite3
  curl
  jsoncpp
  xz
  libdeflate
  openssl@3

Build dependencies (from source)
----------------------------------

Compiler and tools:

  C++17 compiler (GCC >= 10 or Clang >= 12)
  CMake >= 3.16

System packages — Ubuntu 24.04 (x86_64 / aarch64):

  build-essential cmake
  libtbb-dev liblmdb-dev libsqlite3-dev
  libcurl4-openssl-dev libjsoncpp-dev
  zlib1g-dev libbz2-dev liblzma-dev libdeflate-dev autoconf

  Additional for ikafssnhttpd:
    libdrogon-dev uuid-dev libmariadb-dev libyaml-cpp-dev
    libbrotli-dev libhiredis-dev libpq-dev

System packages — Ubuntu 22.04 (x86_64 / aarch64):

  build-essential cmake
  libtbb-dev liblmdb-dev libsqlite3-dev
  libcurl4-openssl-dev libjsoncpp-dev
  zlib1g-dev libbz2-dev liblzma-dev libdeflate-dev autoconf
  libssl-dev uuid-dev

  Note: ikafssnhttpd cannot be built on Ubuntu 22.04
  (Drogon is not packaged for this release). Build with -DBUILD_HTTPD=OFF.

System packages — macOS (Homebrew):

  cmake tbb lmdb sqlite3 curl jsoncpp
  xz libdeflate autoconf automake libtool openssl@3

  Additional for ikafssnhttpd:
    drogon

Source-built libraries:

  NCBI C++ Toolkit 30.0.0  — BLAST DB access
  Parasail 2.6.2           — Stage 3 pairwise alignment
  htslib 1.23              — SAM/BAM output
